#Spam Classifier using NLP 


In this repo I have done Spam classifier using Natural Language Processing . This is my first project in NLP . 

 NLP techniques used like 
       tokenization ,
       stemming , 
       lemmatization , 
       Bag of Words ,
       Tf-idf.
       
I have used colab for this project . spam-classifier-using-NLP.ipynb contains the code        
       
       
